column1: That's a wrap! @DrBiden and my wife Rose finished a three city campaign trip in Texas today - El Paso Dallas and Houston. Your vote is your voice. #EarlyVote #texasforbiden https://t.co/dhjIN1Z1lO
Rose with @DrBiden & El Paso Leaders at stop one of three in Texas. Let's turn Texas Blue! #ElPasoVotes #ElPasoStrong #EarlyVote https://t.co/IGn5Ny2kJ9

I dropped my wife Rose off at the airport this morning. She'll be traveling with Dr. Jill Biden to Houston Dallas and El Paso to speak with voters about what's at stake in this election. Wishing them a safe trip! Stay posted for campaign updates! #EarlyVote #texasblue #JoeBiden https://t.co/B7Pkws6J87
Happy Independence Day! 🎆  Please stay safe and responsible as you celebrate this 4th of July weekend. https://t.co/ypCABRV3LK
This afternoon I’ll be introducing my friend @JoeBiden before he speaks at the @texasdemocrats State Convention. Watch live at 12:30 today: https://t.co/6SoFXs6NTc #TDP20

Nurses are critical to providing accessible quality health care. Thank you for everything you’re doing to keep our communities healthy and safe. #ThankYouNurses #NationalNursesDay https://t.co/776STj5qTT

About to start our live town hall with @JoeBiden @LULAC and my colleagues in Congress. Join us at 11 AM CT as we answer questions about protecting essential workers during #COVID19: https://t.co/KiDjzBtXuX
Looking forward to joining @LULAC and @JoeBiden for a live town hall tomorrow. RSVP below to join us virtually. https://t.co/6FOowi87sK

Texas Mobile Testing Teams are providing #COVID19 testing at locations across the state. If you’re experiencing symptoms visit https://t.co/YWYBwMNCPr to make an appointment and be sure to contact your healthcare professional.

Testing for #COVID19 is critical before schools and businesses open again. Thank you to the experts who joined my Telephone Town Hall to answer your questions from across #TX34.   https://t.co/RuCnf9usu5

Rose and I are wishing you a Happy Easter! We hope you and your family are healthy and safe. Also thinking of all our health care and grocery workers and everyone working today to provide the necessities during this unprecedented time. https://t.co/vh5JovP1P5

Congratulations to @JoeBiden! I’m proud to have spent time campaigning with you and Jill in Texas and across the country this year. I know you can unite this country as our nominee. https://t.co/pLo4Bo1cbz

We depend on grocery store workers and everyone in the food supply chain to keep the shelves stocked and our families fed. You are an essential part of our communities everyday. Thank you! https://t.co/YE0wTPMkOK
Thank you to all the healthcare professionals working around the clock to save lives and fight #COVID19. Your bravery and dedication is inspiring. https://t.co/M7uuvyOYcE

With #COVID19 spreading across Texas we need decisive action from @GovAbbott to expand #Medicaid permanently. Every Texan needs access to health care to help diagnose treat and stop the spread of this virus. https://t.co/jbHo1wuqbt
The Rio Grande Valley needs additional resources and more #COVID19 testing sites. I’ve asked @GovAbbott for the state to make this a priority before it’s too late: https://t.co/ThYv3mtmeD

Last week I was proud to support a #COVID19 relief package and will continue working with my colleagues to ensure our communities have resources to address this pandemic. Please visit our website for more local resources: https://t.co/B6Q4lYtPJt

Thank you #TX34! It was an honor to have your support last night and I can’t wait to see what we accomplish together. Stand with us all the way through November by signing up at https://t.co/JjuHU9L2RL.
Polls are open in Texas! It’s been an honor to represent #TX34 and I hope I can count on your support today. Find your polling place and vote before 7:00 pm tonight: https://t.co/dEGWb58YWa

This country needs a president with a sense of humanity and a sense of service. @JoeBiden is that person.   In the face of challenges he has always persevered and his leadership has never wavered. #WeKnowJoe https://t.co/DDbYw4fgGf
Congratulations to @JoeBiden on a strong showing in the #NVcaucus. Onto South Carolina and Super Tuesday! https://t.co/b4GzIY7rKu
Back with @JoeForNV and @DinaTitus. This team is organized and ready for the #NVcaucus. https://t.co/dzPJSYThL0

Early voting has started in Texas! It’s been an honor to represent #TX34 and with your help I look forward to continuing to be your voice in Congress. Find your early voting location and make a plan to vote today: https://t.co/JBk8gAX1kk

Thanks to team @JoeForNV for inviting me to join them over the weekend. It was great to knock doors with @EricGarcetti and visit with caucus-goers about why @JoeBiden is the best candidate to build the coalition we need to take on Trump. #NVcaucus https://t.co/jvUPFl5B2v
Our new website is launched and ready for you to visit! Get involved learn about what we’ve been doing in the district and get involved: https://t.co/JjuHUa2DJj

We’ve stood up to this administration’s attempts to waive critical environmental regulations for a border wall and will continue to stand against threats to these sensitive environments. Thanks to the @SierraClub for recognizing the work we’re doing in South Texas. https://t.co/5gREWZRMZa
I think the Texas Democratic primary will for the first time in decades determine the next presidential election.
In Bondurant Iowa with team @JoeBiden for the #iacaucus. https://t.co/zmDmwmSXXN

Yesterday I joined @DrBiden in Muscatine Iowa to discuss how critical it is for our country to protect agriculture and return certainty to these markets. We can’t leave rural America behind. #IAcaucus https://t.co/FTaCFy5Ca1
Joining @DrBiden in Iowa ahead of Monday’s #IAcaucus. @JoeBiden is the experienced leader our nation needs - looking forward to meeting caucus-goers across Iowa all weekend. https://t.co/cnJ2TUoMpG

Honored to receive the support of the @TexasAFLCIO COPE committee. We need to continue fighting for fair wages safe working conditions and economic opportunity in #TX34 and across our state. https://t.co/VT8RhEkINz
Proud to recognize our brave Vietnam veterans in #TX34!  "Really an honor for all of us here to be recognized by the way we were today it's a beautiful thing"  https://t.co/PaQryRWZu6
